OL,6,FA driver who deliberately knocked over
OL,7,Fa motorcyclist near Worthing has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FSussex Police said Darren Kay was
OL,11,Fangry at a motorcyclist filtering in
OL,12,Ftraffic on the A259 at Ferring in
OL,13,FMarch last year.
OL,15,FHe caught up with the rider by
OL,16,Fundertaking vehicles in the outside
OL,17,Flane. His vehicle then swerved towards
OL,18,Fthe rider to knock him off.
