OL,3,CDriver who deliberately knocked over
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist near Worthing jailed
OL,6,FThe rider, a 34-year-old man from
OL,7,FLancing, suffered life-changing
OL,8,Finjuries and was taken to hospital
OL,9,Fwith a bleed on the brain.
OL,11,FKay claimed to officers at the scene
OL,12,Fthat he had not seen the motorcycle
OL,13,Fpassing on his inside.
OL,15,FHowever, his own dashcam footage
OL,16,Frecorded how he had pursued the rider
OL,17,Fand said foul mouthed abuse at the
OL,18,Fmoment of impact.
