OL,3,CDriver who deliberately knocked over
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist near Worthing jailed
OL,6,FKay, 53, admitted causing serious
OL,7,Finjury by dangerous driving at Lewes
OL,8,FCrown Court.
OL,10,FInvestigating officer, Sergeant Mark
OL,11,FFarrow from the Roads Policing Unit,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Kay drove dangerously and
OL,13,Fdeliberately to knock over the rider
OL,14,Fof the motorcycle.
OL,16,F"The collision has had a long term
OL,17,Fimpact on his victim who was not able
OL,18,Fto return to his employment for eight
OL,19,Fmonths.
