OL,3,CDriver who deliberately knocked over
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist near Worthing jailed
OL,6,F"Kay's road rage has had a life-
OL,7,Fchanging impact.
OL,9,F"His driving was appalling and
OL,10,Fcompletely unacceptable. He is
OL,11,Fextremely fortunate not to have caused
OL,12,Fa fatality. So we are pleased he is
OL,13,Fnow serving a significant custodial
OL,14,Fsentence, and that a dangerous driver
OL,15,Fhas been taken off our roads."
OL,17,FKay, formerly of Onslow Drive,
OL,18,FFerring, was sentenced to three years
OL,19,Fand two months in prison. He was also
OL,20,Fdisqualified from driving for four
OL,21,Fyears and seven months.
